# Time Complexity

| Operation            | Complexity |
| -------------------- | ---------- |
| Sorting restrictions | O(m log m) |
| Left pass            | O(m)       |
| Right pass           | O(m)       |
| Peak calculation     | O(m)       |

Overall:

```text
Time Complexity: O(m log m)
```

where

```text
m = len(restrictions) + 2
```

